{"tid":1814242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗兵法-鬼又係我人又係我","createTime":"2020-01-06T23:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T01:12:47.000Z","uid":8170,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a37f9c2d012dee1b805046582b5e0255c4d20e","tid":1814242,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:48:32.000Z","msg":"再暗黑啲諗（狗本身就黑）<br />\n裝修嘅係鬼，高調捉鬼嘅都係鬼。<br />\n之後狗扮有幾隊勇武高調退場。<br />\n然後鬼就冇後顧之憂，可以大量出鬼，好似而家啲便衣咁。<br />\n<br />\n全個劇本共通點係「高調」。<br />\n明明講咗話要靜靜雞，突然做咁多咁高調嘢？"},{"pid":"e0007a98ef3b238662e12fbb88126b557a1d9ef5","tid":1814242,"uid":59976,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:50:52.000Z","msg":"話退出果堆擺明對家扮, 真勇武點會少少野就退出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524f960030f540bcae65136d0deba8b948134f0e","tid":1814242,"uid":31200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:52:02.000Z","msg":"咪又係玩分化割席，冇第二招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ab882243a9673bf6d5a40bf1d35482a4557f6a","tid":1814242,"uid":8170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:16:17.000Z","msg":"一陣又畀人話提出問題又冇solution...<br />\n<br />\n嗱，鬼就一定有，捉定係利用，一線之差，聽過養鬼仔未？有人裝修就打氣，萬一佢真係鬼，呢啲就係證據。"},{"pid":"6e2630188bdc088f2f218385ec9c59a9304b802d","tid":1814242,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e55beefd8e4bf2ec2681a0b5e7fb565f07a83a5","tid":1814242,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba61ca3fa49130af74c67a827cf7a045c2278d1e","tid":1814242,"uid":77355,"like":0,"